{{!--
  component-extended-fields  –  default (no-op) partial.

  System adapters that declare extra component fields via
  SystemAdapter.getComponentSchemaExtensions() should override this partial
  via ShipCombat.registerPartialOverride("component-extended-fields", path)
  in their "init" hook, and render any system.extended.* fields there.

  Context available:
    slot   – component slot string ("weapon", "armour", "engine", ...)
    system – full item system data (access extended fields as system.extended.*)
--}}
